search: search index="summary_indexers" | timechart partial=f span=30m per_second(kb) as KBps | addinfo | eval marker = if(_time < info_min_time + 7*86400, "last week", "this week") | eval _time = if(_time < info_min_time + 7*86400, _time + 7*86400+1800, _time+1800) | chart median(KBps) by _time marker
report_search: timechart  partial=f span=30m per_second(kb) as KBps  | addinfo  | eval  marker = if(_time < info_min_time + 7*86400, "last week", "this week")  | eval  _time = if(_time < info_min_time + 7*86400, _time + 7*86400+1800, _time+1800)  | chart  median(KBps) by _time marker
